        <mxCell id="foot" value="The PEP asks, the PDP decides, the PAP supplies the rules, the PIP supplies the facts. Decoupling enforcement from decision lets policy change without redeploying the app." style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=10;fontColor=#4f46e5;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
